name: Mochi Inu
description: Mochi puts your NFTs and long-tail assets to work as collateral while maintaining exposure to their long-term value. An autonomously governed protocol, Mochi bridges the gap between NFTs and DeFi to pioneer a new way to maximize the utility of emerging digital assets. Mochi Protocol Unlocks Productivity in Long-Tail Crypto-Assets With A Next-Gen Fully-Backed Stable Decentralized Currency.
